OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FExtreme weather is causing disruption
OL,7,Facross the region as scores of schools
OL,8,Fhave announced they will close for the
OL,9,Fnext few days with temperatures
OL,10,Fexpected to hit record highs.
OL,12,FA rare red weather warning for extreme
OL,13,Fheat is in place across the South West
OL,14,Fand the UK Health Security Agency
OL,15,F(UKHSA) has said there is a risk to
OL,16,Flife even for healthy people.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
