FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FThe Met Office's red alert will last
OL,7,Funtil 9pm on Thursday 25 June and
OL,8,Fcovers Wiltshire, Gloucestershire,
OL,9,FBristol and the eastern half of
OL,10,FSomerset.
OL,12,FThe agency warns that "substantial
OL,13,Fchanges" in working practices and
OL,14,Fdaily routines will be required, and
OL,15,Findicates a high risk of failure of
OL,16,Fheat-sensitive systems and equipment,
OL,17,Fbringing the loss of power and other
OL,18,Fessential services, such as water,
OL,19,Felectricity, gas or mobile phone
OL,20,Fservices.
OL,26,@tD@WOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
