OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the UKHSA red alert lasts
OL,7,Funtil 11pm on Thursday and covers the
OL,8,Fentirety of the South West, with a
OL,9,Fpredicted significantly increased
OL,10,Fdemand on all health and social care
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FSome 100 schools will be at least
OL,14,Fpartly closed in Somerset, as will
OL,15,Fmore than 80 in Gloucestershire,
OL,16,Faccording to council data.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FMany have explicitly cited red weather
OL,7,Fwarnings and extreme heat for the
OL,8,Freasons behind closures, with some
OL,9,Fexplaining classrooms lack air
OL,10,Fconditioning and that travel to and
OL,11,Ffrom school could be risky in the high
OL,12,Ftemperatures.
OL,14,FExtend Learning Academies Network,
OL,15,Fwhich runs nine primary schools across
OL,16,Fnorth Somerset, said in a letter to
OL,17,Fparents and carers that the schools
OL,18,Fwill be closed all day on Wednesday
OL,19,Fand Thursday "due to the forecast
OL,20,Fsevere heat".
OL,26,@{D@NOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,F"The safety of our pupils, staff and
OL,7,Ffamilies remains our top priority,"
OL,8,Fthe trust added.
OL,10,F"We understand that these closures may
OL,11,Fcause inconvenience, but this decision
OL,12,Fhas been made to ensure the wellbeing
OL,13,Fof everyone in our school community."
OL,15,FWessex Learning Trust, which runs 23
OL,16,Facademies in the South West, announced
OL,17,Fin a post on Instagram that schools
OL,18,Fwill be closed on Wednesday and
OL,19,FThursday "to keep children, families
OL,20,Fand staff safe".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]rD@AOUuD@eO]{D@JOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
