OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FThe trust said pupils will receive
OL,7,Fwork during the closure period and
OL,8,Ffamilies will be contacted about any
OL,9,Ftrips, visits or events that may be
OL,10,Faffected.
OL,12,FNetwork Rail has warned there would be
OL,13,F"significant disruption" as it imposes
OL,14,Fspeed restrictions to minimise the
OL,15,Frisk from heat-related issues such as
OL,16,Fbuckled rails and sagging overhead
OL,17,Felectric wires.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
