CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FThose with a ticket are being allowed
OL,7,Fto travel earlier in the day when the
OL,8,Ftemperatures are lower and if they no
OL,9,Flonger want to travel, they can get a
OL,10,Ffull refund without paying a fee.
OL,12,FGreat Western Railway has issued a
OL,13,Fplea for its services to be used for
OL,14,F"essential travel only" on Wednesday
OL,15,Fand Thursday. The AA is reminding
OL,16,Fdrivers of the strain the heat puts on
OL,17,Fvehicles.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
