OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,FWith temperatures exceeding 30
OL,7,Fdegrees, the RNLI is warning of the
OL,8,Fdangers of swimming or jumping into
OL,9,Fopen water.
OL,11,FRoss Macleod, RNLI Water Safety
OL,12,FManager, said: "The sea or open water
OL,13,Fmay look inviting during hot weather,
OL,14,Fbut it remains cold enough year-round
OL,15,Fto trigger cold water shock, which can
OL,16,Fcause uncontrollable gasping,
OL,17,Fincreased heart rate, and can lead to
OL,18,Fpanic and drowning very quickly. It's
OL,19,Fbest to enter the water slowly to
OL,20,Fgradually acclimatise.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,F"Anyone who finds themselves in danger
OL,7,Fin the water should fight the panic
OL,8,Finstinct and Float to Live ` try to
OL,9,Frelax and float on their back, with
OL,10,Fhead tilted back, gently moving their
OL,11,Fhands and legs to help them stay
OL,12,Fafloat. This buys valuable time to get
OL,13,Fyour breathing back under control,
OL,14,Fbefore then calling for help or
OL,15,Fswimming to safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,F"If you see someone else in danger `
OL,7,Fdo not enter the water yourself as you
OL,8,Fcould also end up in serious
OL,9,Fdifficulty. Instead, remember phone,
OL,10,Ffloat, throw ` phone 999 or 112 and
OL,11,Fask for the Coastguard; tell the
OL,12,Fstruggling person to float; throw them
OL,13,Fsomething buoyant, like a life ring.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
