OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782402488
OL,3,CRare red heat alert warns of 'risk to
OL,4,Clife' across the South West
OL,6,F"If you are visiting the coast this
OL,7,Fweekend, the safest option is a
OL,8,Flifeguarded beach, where you should
OL,9,Fswim between the red and yellow flags.
OL,10,FIf you can't choose a lifeguarded
OL,11,Fbeach, find out about your chosen
OL,12,Fbeach before you visit ` check weather
OL,13,Fand tide times and read local safety
OL,14,Fsignage."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
